---
const pageTitle = "Pablos Zombos";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <title>{pageTitle}</title>
  </head>
      <body>
        <header class="project-hero">
          <h1>{pageTitle}</h1>
          <div class="project-meta">
            <span><strong>Type:</strong> Video Game</span>
            <span><strong>Timeline:</strong> 2 Weeks</span>
            <span><strong>Purpose:</strong> Free Time Practice</span>
          </div>
        </header>

                    <section class="description-box">
                      <p>
                        Pablos Zombos is a top down 2D pixel art zombie shooter game made in GameMaker Studio 2 and in the GML coding language.
                        A friend created the art while I focused on programming and level design and narrative.
                      </p>
                      <p>
                        It taught me how to use trigonometry to calculate the direction of bullets, use spawners for
                        enemies in specific rooms, and make more completed enemy AI.
                      </p>
                    </section>

                    <div class="play-area">
                      <a href="https://arcrux2.github.io/pablosZombos/" target="_blank" class="play-button">
                        <span></span> Play Pablos Zombos
                      </a>
                    </div>

                <figure class="screenshot-card">
                    <img src="/pablosZombos/menuPZ.png" alt="Menu" />
                      <figcaption>
                        Pablos Zombos has the player enter a building full of Zombos
                        where they must go room to room clearing out the Zombos inside. The
                        building is based on a warehouse my team mate and I used to work in.
                        There are 4 different Zombos that the player will encounter; The
                        basic Zombo, the Fat Zombo that is slower but does more damage,
                         the fast Ninja Zombo and the Wizard Zombo. The player must go room to room
                          until they get to the next floor level through the elevator
                          in order to find their friend Pablo who was taken into the
                          building and turned into a Zombo.
                      </figcaption>
               </figure>

               <figure class="multi-image-card">
                  <div class="image-group">
                    <img src="/pablosZombos/door1PZ.png" alt="Door Showcase 1" />
                    <img src="/pablosZombos/door2PZ.png" alt="Door Showcase 2" />
                  </div>
                  <figcaption>
                    These two photos showcase how the rooms lock the player in with the
                    enemies and don't open until all of them are defeated.
                  </figcaption>
               </figure>

               <figure class="screenshot-card">
                    <img src="/pablosZombos/spawnerCodePZ.png" alt="Spawner Code" />
                      <figcaption>
                        This is the code for the spawner object that creates
                        the enemies and confines them to the room the player is in.
                      </figcaption>
               </figure>

               <figure class="screenshot-card">
                    <img src="/pablosZombos/playerCodePZ.png" alt="Player Code" />
                        <figcaption>
                            This is the code for the player.
                        </figcaption>
               </figure>

               <figure class="multi-image-card">
                   <div class="image-group">
                    <img src="/pablosZombos/shotPZ.png" alt="Shot 1" />
                    <img src="/pablosZombos/shotgunPZ.png" alt="Shot 2" />
                   </div>
                      <figcaption>
                        These photos showcase the two different modes the
                        player's weapon can be in: Gun as a rapid fire
                        low damage shot and Shotgun as a spread high damage shot.
                      </figcaption>
               </figure>

               <figure class="screenshot-card">
                    <img src="/pablosZombos/bulletCodePZ.png" alt="Bullet Code" />
                      <figcaption>
                        This is the code for the bullets.
                      </figcaption>
               </figure>

               <figure class="screenshot-card">
                    <img src="/pablosZombos/ninjaPZ.png" alt="Ninja Zombie" />
                      <figcaption>
                        The Ninja Zombo is a faster version of the normal zombos
                      </figcaption>
               </figure>

               <figure class="screenshot-card">
                    <img src="/pablosZombos/wizardPZ.png" alt="Wizard Zombie" />
                      <figcaption>
                        The Wizard Zombo switches from slowly following the
                        player and stopping to shoot a deadly fire ball.
                      </figcaption>
               </figure>

               <figure class="screenshot-card">
                    <img src="/pablosZombos/warpPZ.png" alt="Warp Object" />
                       <figcaption>
                        At the end of each level in the last room after all Zombos
                        have been defeated an elevator takes the player to the
                        next floor of the building.
                       </figcaption>
               </figure>

               <figure class="screenshot-card">
                    <img src="/pablosZombos/bossPZ.png" alt="Boss Fight" />
                       <figcaption>
                        The highest floor has the final boss, Pablo,
                        the player's friend who was turned into a Zombo.
                        Pablo shoots green liquid filled syringes to try
                        and turn the player into a Zombo.
                       </figcaption>
               </figure>

               <figure class="screenshot-card">
                    <img src="/pablosZombos/endPZ.png" alt="Ending" />
                       <figcaption>
                        Once Pablo is defeated the player turns him back to human
                        to beat the game.
                       </figcaption>
               </figure>

                    <footer class="bottom-nav">
                      <a href="/" class="home-button">Home</a>
                    </footer>
      </body>
</html>

<style>
.project-hero {
    background-color: #166534;
    border: 4px solid #22c55e;
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 40px 20px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.2);
  }

.project-hero h1 {
    color: #ffffff;
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin: 0;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
  }

.project-meta {
    margin-top: 15px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 20px;
    color: #bbf7d0;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

.project-meta span {
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    padding: 5px 15px;
    border-radius: 20px;
  }

.description-box {
    background-color: #262626;
    border: 4px solid #3f3f46;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 25px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #d1d5db;
  }

.description-box p {
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  .play-area {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 40px 0;
    }

    .play-button {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 15px;
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, #16a34a, #22c55e);
      color: #052e16;
      padding: 18px 40px;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      text-decoration: none;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      border-radius: 8px;
      border: 2px solid #14532d;

      box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.4), inset 0 2px 2px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
      transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
    }

    .play-button span {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
    }

    .play-button:hover {
      transform: scale(1.05);
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, #22c55e, #4ade80);
      box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.8);
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .play-button:active {
      transform: scale(0.98);
      }

body {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 20px;
    font-family: arial;
    background-color: #1a1a1a;
    color: #f3f4f6;
  }

.screenshot-card {
    background-color: #2d2d2d;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
    text-align: center;
  }

.screenshot-card img {
    max-width: 100%;
    border-radius: 8px;
    height: auto;
  }

.screenshot-card figcaption {
    margin-top: 15px;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #a7f3d0;
  }

.multi-image-card {
    background-color: #2d2d2d;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
  }

.image-group {
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
  }

.image-group img {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 300px;
    max-width: 48%;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

figcaption {
    margin-top: 15px;
    text-align: center;
    color: #a7f3d0;
    font-style: italic;
  }

.bottom-nav {
    margin-top: 60px;
    padding: 40px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid #374151;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

a {
    color: #4f46e5;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

.home-button {
    display: inline-block;
    background-color: #06a94d;
    color: white;
    padding: 16px 32px;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 50px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 255, 0, 0.4);
  }

.home-button:hover {
    background-color: #06c258;
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 255, 0, 0.6);
  }
</style>